Integrate Campaign with VECTR
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Install and configure VECTR for Red Team operation tracking
Document Red Team tactics using the MITRE ATT&CK framework
Create Python scripts to interact with VECTR's REST API
Log Red Team activities systematically during campaigns
Generate automated reports from campaign data
Prerequisites
Before starting this lab, students should have:

Basic understanding of Red Team operations and MITRE ATT&CK framework
Familiarity with Linux command line and Docker
Basic Python programming knowledge and REST API concepts
Understanding of JSON data formats
